Enable various tests under ASan

Setting "ASAN_OPTIONS=handle_segv=0" across the board fixes a lot of
tests, and it allows us to enable sel_ldr's platform qualification
test.

BUG=http://code.google.com/p/nativeclient/issues/detail?id=2717
TEST=no ASan trybots, so: "small_tests medium_tests large_tests --asan"
  locally on x86-64 Linux and x86-32 Mac

